review_blob: A cloudy beer with an overly foamy head, this is just too much. Its got an overwhelming taste of wheat and a bitter aftertaste. I wont need another one of these.
beer_name: Rock Art Magnumus ete Tomahawkus ESB2 Ale

review_blob: This is a very, very sweet lambic. It has only the barest hint of the sour aftertaste that I expect from a proper lambic. This is more like a juice box than a proper beer.
I love the fact that I can get the Pennant Ale 55 at the bodega across the street from my house. This is a great, light ale and goes well with BBQ.
A sweet and slightly wheaty ale, the Tripel has a lightly bitter aftertaste. Very nice.
It has an amber appearance and a clean, hoppy taste. Its a very nice blonde. Have several!
